        <content type="html" xml:base="https://aw2.help/builds/heal-quick-troubadour/">&lt;p&gt;The Troubadour has an easy design such that when you randomly mash all the buttons, you&#x27;d provide all the right boons and heals. This build has selected utilities for minimal cognitive complexity, such that the hardest part of playing this build is enduring the out-of-sync music throughout the fight.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;While this guide assumes no weapon swap is needed, if you take an off-tank role, you may consider swapping rifle to other alternatives.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
