&lt;hr&#x2F;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;small&gt;This is a low toughness set-up.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;alternative&quot;&gt;Alternative&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Weapon swap is optional. Consider scepter and shield for tanking and focus for additional CC&#x2F;pulls.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;table class=&quot;weapontable&quot;&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;th&gt;Weapon&lt;&#x2F;th&gt;&lt;th&gt;Type&lt;&#x2F;th&gt;&lt;th&gt;Stat&lt;&#x2F;th&gt;&lt;th&gt;Upgrade&lt;&#x2F;th&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;&lt;&#x2F;thead&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;
