&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;small&gt;&lt;em&gt;Shield is better used for tanking and focus is useful for pulling adds. Alternate weapon sets should be prioritised based on utility requirements.&lt;&#x2F;em&gt;&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;clear:both;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;budget-options&quot;&gt;Budget Options&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Replace any of the sigil with &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;24551&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Superior Sigil of Water&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;consumables&quot;&gt;Consumables&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;91690&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Bowl of Fruit Salad with Mint Garnish OR &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;68634&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Delicious Rice Ball &lt;em&gt;(budget alternative)&lt;&#x2F;em&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;81157&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Magnanimous Maintenance Oil OR &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;87329&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Holographic Super Drumstick &lt;em&gt;(budget alternative)&lt;&#x2F;em&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&quot;build&quot;&gt;Build&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Heal Quickness Build&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre data-lang=&quot;chatlink&quot; class=&quot;language-chatlink z-code&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-chatlink&quot; data-lang=&quot;chatlink&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-source z-chatlink&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-definition z-string z-begin&quot;&gt;[&amp;amp;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;DQctOhcqSTptAQ8BUx2GAYQdgQFrHWsBbR28AQAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAABWQAA&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-definition z-string z-end&quot;&gt;]&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;div data-armory-embed=&#x27;skills&#x27; data-armory-ids=&#x27;10213,76850,76611,77178,76971&#x27;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;&lt;div data-armory-embed=&#x27;specializations&#x27; data-armory-ids=&#x27;45,23,73&#x27; data-armory-45-traits=&#x27;675,668,1687&#x27; data-armory-23-traits=&#x27;738,740,1866&#x27; data-armory-73-traits=&#x27;2326,2367,2441&#x27;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;rotation-and-utilities&quot;&gt;Rotation and Utilities&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There is no fixed rotation for this build. Even if you randomly press buttons you will still provide boons and adequate heals.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;quickness&quot;&gt;Quickness&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will need to use the following for quickness:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76552&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Lively Lute&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76931&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Crescendo (while as many instruments are playing as possible)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;swiftness&quot;&gt;Swiftness&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10213&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Mantra of Recovery&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10214&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Power Return&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your healing skills trigger &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;101116&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Relic of Febe to grant swiftness, use them off cooldown.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;small&gt;&lt;em&gt;Shield or Focus can partially cover quickness, allowing you to drop &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;101116&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Relic of Febe&lt;&#x2F;em&gt;&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;general-rotation&quot;&gt;General rotation&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generate Notes (Clones)
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;71897&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Journey (R2)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;72007&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Phantasmal Sharpshooter (R4)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10213&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Mantra of Recovery -&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10214&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Power Return (Heal)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Any tale with instrument-pairing&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Spend Notes to play Instruments as soon as they recharged (2 or more notes)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76931&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Crescendo when you have 3 or more instruments playing&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You provide lots of boons and healing through instruments, rifle skills and utilities provide even more of them.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;utilty&quot;&gt;Utilty&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You may replace skill slot 9 with any of the following:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;77178&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Tale of the Valiant Marshal for a stun break + short stability + additional notes&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10237&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Mantra of Concentration for permanent stability&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10207&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Mantra of Resolve for heavy condi cleanses&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10302&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Feedback for reflects&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
